medicareAdvantagePlansContent: Medicare Advantage plans cover your hospital (Medicare Part A) and doctor (Medicare Part B), just like Original Medicare, But many offer additional benefits, as well.
medicareSupplementPlansContent: Medicare Supplement Plans provide additional help with some of the out-of-pocket expenses not paid by Medicare Parts A & B
prescriptionDrugPlansContent: Medicare prescription drug plans (Medicare Part D) help cover the cost of your prescription drugs.
